data.description: This 1114 square foot single family home has 3 bedrooms and 1.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 1512 N Main St, Temple, TX 76501.
data.whatILove: This home is located in North Temple, right next to Miller Park which is great for anyone who loves outdoor activities! between Hot summer sounds, which provides free live music events, movie in the park and a great fireworks show twice a year it is a great place to spend some time. The park also features a great walking path and splash pad for the kids. This home has a large and front backyard which are great for getting outside and having plenty of room. The home has great laminate floors that look like hardwood but are so much more durable. This home is also located in the school district for the newly renovated Jefferson Elementary school
